import React from 'react'
import { Route, Switch } from 'react-router-dom'
import Airlines from '../components/Airlines/Airlines'

const App = () => {
  return(
    <Switch>
      <Route exact path="/">
        <Airlines />
      </Route>
      <Route exact path="/:slug" component="Airline" />
    </Switch>
  )
}

export default App
